document_data.name: Carliela Benstyl
document_data.mainbody:
'''Carliela Benstyl''' was a [[human]] [[rogue]] and [[fighter]] and leader of the [[Merchants' Guild (Veltalar)|Merchants' Guild]] of [[Veltalar|Velprintalar]] (now known as Old Velprintalar) in [[1374 DR]]. She was an influential member of the [[Sons of Hoar]].
